Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女与战车 OVA第六话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.56,0:01:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会战争！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决赛真的辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于大家出色的表现 我校成功拿到了优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战车道世界中默默无闻的我校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁能想到居然能击败如此多豪强学校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一次会载入高中战车道历史的壮举
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也全靠..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃桃 讲太长了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就开始庆功会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会长 您请
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 不用被废校真的太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么干杯吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样而已吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干..干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向校园的风气干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向战车和排球部干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
